# TanStack Query Patterns

Server state'in TEK aracı. Zustand'a server data koyma — stale data garanti.

## Query Key Factory

Her modül için type-safe key factory:

```typescript
// lib/query-keys.ts
export const queryKeys = {
  auth: {
    me: () => ['auth', 'me'] as const,
  },
  users: {
    all: () => ['users'] as const,
    lists: () => [...queryKeys.users.all(), 'list'] as const,
    list: (filters?: UserListFilters) => 
      [...queryKeys.users.lists(), filters ?? {}] as const,
    details: () => [...queryKeys.users.all(), 'detail'] as const,
    detail: (id: string) => [...queryKeys.users.details(), id] as const,
    sessions: (id: string) => [...queryKeys.users.detail(id), 'sessions'] as const,
  },
  processes: {
    all: () => ['processes'] as const,
    lists: () => [...queryKeys.processes.all(), 'list'] as const,
    list: (filters?: ProcessFilters) => 
      [...queryKeys.processes.lists(), filters ?? {}] as const,
    details: () => [...queryKeys.processes.all(), 'detail'] as const,
    detail: (displayId: string) => 
      [...queryKeys.processes.details(), displayId] as const,
  },
  tasks: {
    all: () => ['tasks'] as const,
    mine: (filters?: TaskFilters) => 
      [...queryKeys.tasks.all(), 'mine', filters ?? {}] as const,
    detail: (id: string) => [...queryKeys.tasks.all(), 'detail', id] as const,
  },
  // ... diğer modüller
} as const;
```

Hierarchical yapı invalidation'ı kolaylaştırır:
- `invalidateQueries({ queryKey: queryKeys.users.all() })` — tüm user queries invalidate
- `invalidateQueries({ queryKey: queryKeys.users.lists() })` — sadece list queries
- `invalidateQueries({ queryKey: queryKeys.users.detail(id) })` — tek user detail

## Query Hook Pattern

```typescript
// lib/queries/users.ts
import { useQuery } from '@tanstack/react-query';
import { apiClient } from '@/lib/api-client';
import { queryKeys } from '@/lib/query-keys';
import type { UserResponse, UserListQuery } from '@leanmgmt/shared-schemas';

export function useUserQuery(id: string) {
  return useQuery({
    queryKey: queryKeys.users.detail(id),
    queryFn: () => apiClient.get<UserResponse>(`/api/v1/users/${id}`)
      .then((r) => r.data.data),
    enabled: !!id,
    staleTime: 60_000,
  });
}

export function useUserListQuery(filters: UserListQuery) {
  return useQuery({
    queryKey: queryKeys.users.list(filters),
    queryFn: () => apiClient
      .get('/api/v1/users', { params: filters })
      .then((r) => r.data.data),
    placeholderData: keepPreviousData,  // pagination UX
    staleTime: 30_000,
  });
}
```

## Stale Time Guidelines

| Data türü | Stale time |
|---|---|
| Current user (me) | 5 dk |
| User list | 30 sn |
| User detail | 1 dk |
| Process list (my tasks) | 15 sn |
| Process detail | 30 sn |
| Master data (companies, depts) | 10 dk |
| Notifications (unread count) | 20 sn |
| Dashboard widgets | 60 sn |
| Audit log list | 0 (always refetch) |

Real-time ihtiyacı → `refetchInterval`:

```typescript
useQuery({
  queryKey: queryKeys.tasks.mine(),
  queryFn: ...,
  staleTime: 15_000,
  refetchInterval: 30_000,  // background refresh
});
```

## Mutation Pattern

```typescript
// lib/queries/users.ts
export function useCreateUserMutation() {
  const queryClient = useQueryClient();
  return useMutation({
    mutationFn: (input: CreateUserInput) => 
      apiClient.post('/api/v1/users', input).then((r) => r.data.data),
    onSuccess: () => {
      // Tüm user list'leri invalidate (filter kombine sayılmaz)
      queryClient.invalidateQueries({ queryKey: queryKeys.users.lists() });
    },
  });
}

export function useUpdateUserMutation(id: string) {
  const queryClient = useQueryClient();
  return useMutation({
    mutationFn: (input: UpdateUserInput) =>
      apiClient.patch(`/api/v1/users/${id}`, input).then((r) => r.data.data),
    onSuccess: (updated) => {
      // Detay cache'i direct set et (bir fetch kazanırız)
      queryClient.setQueryData(queryKeys.users.detail(id), updated);
      // List cache'leri invalidate (list'te güncel görsün)
      queryClient.invalidateQueries({ queryKey: queryKeys.users.lists() });
    },
  });
}

export function useDeactivateUserMutation() {
  const queryClient = useQueryClient();
  return useMutation({
    mutationFn: ({ id, reason }: { id: string; reason: string }) =>
      apiClient.post(`/api/v1/users/${id}/deactivate`, { reason })
        .then((r) => r.data.data),
    onSuccess: (_, { id }) => {
      queryClient.invalidateQueries({ queryKey: queryKeys.users.detail(id) });
      queryClient.invalidateQueries({ queryKey: queryKeys.users.lists() });
    },
  });
}
```

## Invalidation Rules

Mutation sonrası hangi cache'leri invalidate edeceğin:

| Mutation | Invalidate |
|---|---|
| User create | `users.lists()` |
| User update | `users.detail(id)`, `users.lists()` |
| User deactivate | `users.detail(id)`, `users.lists()` |
| Role assign to user | `users.detail(id)`, `auth.me()` (self ise) |
| Process start | `processes.lists()`, `tasks.mine()` |
| Task claim | `tasks.mine()`, `processes.detail(displayId)` |
| Task complete | `tasks.mine()`, `processes.detail(displayId)` |
| Notification mark read | `notifications.unreadCount()`, `notifications.list()` |

`all()` ile over-invalidate yapma — her query'yi tekrar fetch eder, network waste.

## Optimistic Update

Kritik UX (like button, mark-read notification) için optimistic:

```typescript
export function useMarkNotificationReadMutation() {
  const queryClient = useQueryClient();
  return useMutation({
    mutationFn: (id: string) => 
      apiClient.post(`/api/v1/notifications/${id}/mark-read`),
    
    onMutate: async (id) => {
      await queryClient.cancelQueries({ queryKey: queryKeys.notifications.list() });
      
      const prev = queryClient.getQueryData(queryKeys.notifications.list());
      queryClient.setQueryData(queryKeys.notifications.list(), (old) => {
        return old?.map((n) => n.id === id ? { ...n, isRead: true } : n);
      });
      
      return { prev };  // rollback context
    },
    
    onError: (err, id, context) => {
      // Rollback
      if (context?.prev) {
        queryClient.setQueryData(queryKeys.notifications.list(), context.prev);
      }
      toast.error('Güncelleme başarısız');
    },
    
    onSettled: () => {
      queryClient.invalidateQueries({ queryKey: queryKeys.notifications.list() });
    },
  });
}
```

Optimistic sadece trivial state change'lerde — confirmation gereken işlemlerde kullanma.

## Pagination — Cursor-Based

```typescript
// Simple pagination (not infinite)
const [cursor, setCursor] = useState<string | undefined>();

const { data, isFetching, isPlaceholderData } = useQuery({
  queryKey: queryKeys.users.list({ cursor, limit: 20 }),
  queryFn: () => apiClient.get('/api/v1/users', { 
    params: { cursor, limit: 20 } 
  }).then((r) => r.data.data),
  placeholderData: keepPreviousData,
});

// Next page button
<Button 
  onClick={() => setCursor(data.pagination.nextCursor)}
  disabled={isPlaceholderData || !data?.pagination.hasMore}
>
  Sonraki
</Button>
```

Infinite scroll için `useInfiniteQuery`:

```typescript
const { data, fetchNextPage, hasNextPage } = useInfiniteQuery({
  queryKey: queryKeys.tasks.mine(filters),
  queryFn: ({ pageParam }) => apiClient
    .get('/api/v1/tasks/mine', { params: { cursor: pageParam, ...filters } })
    .then((r) => r.data.data),
  initialPageParam: undefined,
  getNextPageParam: (lastPage) => lastPage.pagination.nextCursor,
});
```

## Query Enable/Disable

Conditional query:

```typescript
// User ID yoksa query çalıştırma
useUserQuery(id);  // içinde `enabled: !!id`

// User authenticated değilse me query çalışmaz
const { accessToken } = useAuthStore();
const { data: me } = useMeQuery({ enabled: !!accessToken });
```

## Error Handling

Global interceptor (`api-client.ts`) 401/403 handle. Query hook'ta `onError` nadir gerekli.

Component'te error göster:

```typescript
const { data, error, isLoading } = useUserListQuery(filters);

if (isLoading) return <UserListSkeleton />;
if (error) return <InlineError message="Kullanıcılar yüklenemedi" onRetry={refetch} />;
if (!data.items.length) return <EmptyState ... />;

return <UserList items={data.items} />;
```

## Default Query Client Config

```typescript
// components/Providers.tsx
const queryClient = new QueryClient({
  defaultOptions: {
    queries: {
      staleTime: 30_000,
      refetchOnWindowFocus: false,  // TR çalışma saatlerinde gereksiz
      retry: (failureCount, error: AxiosError) => {
        if (error.response?.status === 401 || 
            error.response?.status === 403 ||
            error.response?.status === 404) return false;
        return failureCount < 3;
      },
    },
    mutations: {
      retry: false,  // mutation'lar retry olmaz
    },
  },
});
```

## Banned Patterns

- Server data Zustand'a set etmek (sync problemi)
- Raw `fetch()` kullanmak (apiClient axios singleton)
- `useEffect` içinde fetch (TanStack Query kullan)
- Manual cache management (`setQueryData` sadece mutation onSuccess'te)
- Over-invalidation (`invalidateQueries()` no args — tüm cache)
- Query key array literal inline (key factory kullan)
- `staleTime: 0` + `refetchOnMount: always` (büyük cost)
- Suspense hybrid mode (MVP'de `useQuery` default, `useSuspenseQuery` yok)

